meanings: (건물이) collapse, crumble (away), (무게·압력 등으로) give way, (지붕·벽 등이) cave in (=붕괴되다)
(균형·질서·체제 등이) collapse, crumble (away), disintegrate, fall apart, (주식시장 등이) crash

meanings.meaning: the tottering walls of the castle
